summary:
so my dad was like to my family:
“we went to go pick her up from interactive introverts and all the parents could hear from...
body:
so my dad was like to my family:

“we went to go pick her up from interactive introverts and all the parents could hear from outside was screaming. screaming for two gay guys on a stage? i bet those two can’t believe their luck!”

and i was like YES.

  1. dan can’t believe his luck because he found phil
  2. dan and phil created something even though they were put down a lot
  3. their fan base is insane and talented and appreciate them with so much dedication.

even though i know he was being sarcastic, my dad had a point.
